text: Chris Benjamin (born 29 April 1999) is a South African cricketer. He made his first-class debut on 26 March 2019, for Durham MCCU against Durham, as part of the Marylebone Cricket Club University fixtures. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Durham MCCU cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Alumni of Collingwood College, Durham
